login.SLIDES_TEXT_3 = New social learning tools available on Learnpedia enable you and your students to <b>engage</b> and <b>collaborate</b> on any academic subject. Learnpedia helps you stay connected beyond the classroom.
login.SLIDES_TEXT_4 = Results on Learnpedia go a step beyond just displaying the regular marks and ranks. Learnpedia's intelligent <b>algorithms</b> give students their detailed <b>strength, weakness</b> analysis based on their attempt pattern across multiple Tests.

